INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('53', '给小丸子的一封信！', '一个人在海上漂累了的时候，往往想找个心灵港湾去停泊。——大哥', null, '', '<blockquote><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">一个人在海上漂累了的时候，往往想找个心灵港湾去停泊。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ——大哥</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">婉俊：</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">身处这灯火通明和喧嚣的城市，在我的内心深处还是有那么一丝丝的忧伤和孤独，或生命中出现那么一位可爱的人来填补内心的空白，这何尝不是一件快乐的事情呢？</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190304/1551712147.jpg\" title=\"1551712147.jpg\" alt=\"zxc.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">昨天天气很好，很适合去踏青，于是梳洗完头发，画个漂亮的淡妆，穿着大方美丽，今天去哪呢？等坐上了公交，找了一个座位美美的坐了下来，拿起手机这时男朋友发了视频过来，我点开之后，我的嘴角微微一笑。&quot;哇，好漂亮吖，……&quot;，我顿时也害羞的笑了起来，心情大好。坐公交到了曲江，这个时候已经是中午，于吃了个午饭，然后从曲江一路走到大雁塔，我真佩服自己走了这么多的路，这一天走了14公里，一航每天最多才10公里呢，是不是像个&quot;女汉纸&quot;？</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">这几天的确是忙到很晚才休息，昨晚，我们几个人放松一下，吃完饭就去唱歌，我的声音可以说是五音不全，完全不在一个调子上，尽管如此，我还唱了beyond的《海阔天空》《真的爱你》《喜欢你》等，我在唱的时候，在大多数情况下歌词是忘了的。在唱完几首歌之后，我便走出客厅去旁边的小屋和最可爱的人聊天，真是意犹未尽，真想一个吻过去，所有的话都在里边。她说我是傻子，我傻傻的一笑。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">说，了解一个人不光是表面的，它的内在美也是很重要的。两年之前，我们还是陌生人，你不属于我，一次偶然的机会我们有幸认识，或许那个时候我们并未认真的去对待感情这个事情，尤其是陌路人，我记得跟你聊了几天之后便没有下文了，在之后的两年内，你在默默的关注我，我的每一条心情、日志、照片你都留意过，只是没有和我互动，你的空间更新很难，一年更新不了几个，因此我忽视了你的存在。就这样过了730天，我在你的好友里，你也在我的好友里，换句话说，你我潜伏彼此身边两年，只是没说话而已。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">可是，缘分这东西没有人可以弄明白的，一次偶遇，一见钟情……，都能使并无交集的两个人走在一起，携手一生。在我相识的女孩当中，你别具一格，给人一种清新脱俗的感觉。所谓真爱，无非就是恋爱中的两人彼此吸引，交流很畅通、开心、幸福。我们的三观（人生观、价值观、爱情观）不谋而合，正如人们所说的天造地和的一对，亲朋好友们所说的有夫妻相，其实，通过长时间的交流，我们彼此都清楚的明白，只是心照不宣罢了。文静的你，和害羞的你，不善于表达你对我情感，可是我能感受到你对我的爱意和关心以及体贴，我想说的是：一航的一生有你就足够了！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">佛家常说：人生轮回，好比我现在看到的时钟，既是起点也是终点，就像我们的感情一般。我多么的希望我后半生和最可爱的你一起度过，相濡以沫，一不小心白了头，待到黄昏再相遇，你我尽开颜『君开心我随意』。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190304/1551712255.jpg\" title=\"1551712255.jpg\" alt=\"000.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">曾经看过一部韩剧《继承者们》有一集说到：当教授问世间上最美的五个单词是什么，堂下的学生没有一个人回答上海，可是教授给的答案依次是mother、passion 、smile、love、forever，这时，全班所有人沉静了。对于我而言，除了一个我感受不到外，其他的我都做到了，在这里我要谢谢最可爱的你，谢谢我能遇见你，谢谢你在我难过、高兴的时候陪着我，你就是我最忠诚的听众和红颜，我也属于你一个人的舞台。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">在以后的日子里，你的愿望不再是世界和平，不会再是那么的飘渺，我只要你过得开心幸福。以后的生活或许多了一个人，你要开始去适应了，不管做什么事情请不要忽视我的存在，以后你的愿望不要没有我，不管是快乐的忧伤的，我都会陪在你身边的。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">我想，2017年2月，我想对最可爱的你说：&quot;<strong>傻瓜，起来，吃饭啦……，n 55!w ！、n paau ！、 n a^o7 ！还有爱心日志</strong>，还有（<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">❤</span>40）……！&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', '1', 'checked', 'checked', '2017-02-26 23:14:04', '77', '1022', null);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('54', '夜 ', '我踏着快马飞奔而来，夜的温度临至零点，我在远处望你.......', null, '/upload/article/20190307213109.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">我踏着快马飞奔而来，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">夜的温度临至零点，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">我在远处望你，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">你在近处等待，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">夜终究漫长而孤独，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">疲惫的身躯，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">只为有一天能看到黎明，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">莫等闲，不负君。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\"></span></p><hr/><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190307/1551965035.jpg\" title=\"1551965035.jpg\" alt=\"11.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;沪 | 相遇&gt;</strong></span></p>', '1', 'checked', 'checked', '2019-03-09 07:55:39', '85', '66', '2019-03-10 20:10:04');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('55', 'Linux：如何使用navicat连接Mysql', 'Mysql默认只能进行本机访问，所以我们使用navicat进行连接时会失败，我们只需要开启mysql权限就可以了', null, '/upload/article/20190307213808.png', '<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">Mysql默认只能进行本机访问，所以我们使用navicat进行连接时会失败，我们只需要开启mysql权限就可以了</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">1、使用xshell进入Linux下mysql控制台，然后输入一下命令</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; white-space: pre;\"></span>/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql -u root -p<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\">（<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Linux：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">mysql -u root -p</span></span>）</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; white-space: pre;\"></span>GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO &#39;root&#39;@&#39;%&#39; IDENTIFIED BY &#39;password&#39; WITH GRANT OPTION;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">2、再刷新权限</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">FLUSH PRIVILEGES;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">3、Linux下开启3306端口</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">iptables -I INPUT -p tcp --dport 3306 -j ACCEPT</span></p></ul><p><br/></p>', '3', 'checked', '', '2019-03-07 21:38:12', '14', '26', null);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('56', '今夜，无眠', '那个男孩，有没有想起我？\n那个女孩，有没有念叨我？', null, '/upload/article/20190307214355.jpg', '<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">今夜，月圆！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: 隶书, SimLi;\">那个男孩，有没有想起我？<br/>那个女孩，有没有念叨我？<br/>没有我的今夜 ，<br/>有没有看花、赏月、寻北斗？<br/>这样美好的夜，<br/>我突然想要喝酒、睡觉、掉眼泪。<br/><br/>那个女孩，曾教会我爱。<br/>那个男孩，曾教会我成长。<br/>有他们的日子，<br/>我的心暖暖的。<br/>异乡里，想起他们<br/>我咬着牙走了好久。<br/>很抱歉，女孩男孩，<br/>我没努力的文武双全，<br/>让你们担忧至今，牵挂依旧。<br/><br/>那个男孩，<br/>你可知道你帅气到无与伦比。<br/>那个女孩，<br/>你可知道你美丽到无可挑剔。<br/>人生路上，<br/>你们可知道，<br/>我需要你们的一直陪伴。<br/>所以，答应我，<br/>不要不争气的输给岁月，<br/>不要那么匆匆的老去，<br/>让我像孩子般宠爱你们。<br/><br/>今夜，人未眠！</span></p></ul>', '1', 'checked', '', '2019-03-07 21:44:05', '5', '12', null);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('57', 'MySQL：日期和时间戳之间相互转化', '1、获取当前时间+10分钟的时间(SECOND/MINUTE)\nSELECT DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL +10 MINUTE)', null, '/upload/article/20190311165724.jpg', '<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>1、获取当前时间+10分钟的时间(SECOND/MINUTE)</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">SELECT DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL +10 MINUTE);</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190311/1552294614.jpg\" title=\"1552294614.jpg\" alt=\"222.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>2、获取当前时间</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">NOW();</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>3、获取当前时间戳</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">SELECT UNIX_TIMESTAMP(&#39;2018-10-01 12:00:00&#39;) //若没有时间，获取当前时间戳 &nbsp; 1538366400</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">应用：SELECT name,UNIX_TIMESTAMP(time) as time FROM 2019_zf;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>4、将时间戳转化为时间</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">SELECT FROM_UNIXTIME(1538366400)</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">结果：2018-10-01 12:00:00</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">应用：SELECT `name`,`content`,FROM_UNIXTIME(`time`) AS `time` FROM `liuyan`;</span></p><hr/><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">public function QueryFtype($column = &#39;FTYPE&#39;)</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; {</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return &quot;CASE &quot; . $column . &quot;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 1 THEN &#39;操作系统&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 2 THEN &#39;进程&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 3 THEN &#39;文件&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 4 THEN &#39;注册表项&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 5 THEN &#39;IM&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WHEN 6 THEN &#39;IPMAC绑定&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ELSE &#39;&#39;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; END &quot; . $column;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$timeTemp = [</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0 =&gt; $now - 900, //最近15分钟</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1 =&gt; $now - 3600, //最近1小时</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2 =&gt; $now - 6 * 3600, //最近6小时</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3 =&gt; $now - 12 * 3600, //最近12小时</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4 =&gt; $now - 86400, //最近1天</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5 =&gt; $now - 86400 * 7, //最近7天</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6 =&gt; $now - 86400 * 30, //最近30天</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7 =&gt; 1, //全部时间</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8 =&gt; &#39;self&#39;, //自定义时间</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>];</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>if (isset($timeTemp[$get[&#39;time&#39;]]) &amp;&amp; $timeTemp[$get[&#39;time&#39;]] !== &#39;self&#39;) {</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$where .= &quot; AND LOGTIME &gt;= :sta&quot;;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$param[&#39;sta&#39;] = date(&#39;Y-m-d H:i:s&#39;, $timeTemp[$get[&#39;time&#39;]]);</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>} else if (isset($timeTemp[$get[&#39;time&#39;]]) &amp;&amp; $timeTemp[$get[&#39;time&#39;]] == &#39;self&#39; &amp;&amp; !empty($timeScope)) {</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$timeTmp = explode(&#39; - &#39;, $timeScope);</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$where .= &quot; AND LOGTIME &gt;= :sta AND LOGTIME&lt; :end&quot;;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$param[&#39;sta&#39;] = (trim($timeTmp[0]));</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>$param[&#39;end&#39;] = (trim($timeTmp[1]));</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span>}</p>', '3', 'checked', '', '2019-03-11 16:58:44', '34', '24', '2019-03-11 19:51:00');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('58', 'MYSQL 优化常用方法', '对查询进行优化，应尽量避免全表扫描，首先应考虑在 where 及 order by 涉及的列上建立索引', null, '', '<p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">在sql查询中为了提高查询效率，我们常常会采取一些措施对查询语句进行sql优化，下面总结的一些方法，有需要的可以参考参考。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">1.对查询进行优化，应尽量避免全表扫描，首先应考虑在 where 及 order by 涉及的列上建立索引。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">2.应尽量避免在 where 子句中对字段进行 null 值判断，否则将导致引擎放弃使用索引而进行全表扫描，如：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num is null<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">可以在num上设置默认值0，确保表中num列没有null值，然后这样查询：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num=0<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">3.应尽量避免在 where 子句中使用!=或&lt;&gt;操作符，否则将引擎放弃使用索引而进行全表扫描。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">4.应尽量避免在 where 子句中使用 or 来连接条件，否则将导致引擎放弃使用索引而进行全表扫描，如：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num=10 or num=20<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">可以这样查询：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num=10&nbsp;<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">union all&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num=20</span><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; white-space: pre;\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">5.in 和 not in 也要慎用，否则会导致全表扫描，如：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num in(1,2,3)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">对于连续的数值，能用 between 就不要用 in 了：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num between 1 and 3<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">6.下面的查询也将导致全表扫描：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where name like &#39;%abc%&#39;<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">7.应尽量避免在 where 子句中对字段进行表达式操作，这将导致引擎放弃使用索引而进行全表扫描。如：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num/2=100<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">应改为:<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where num=100*2<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">8.应尽量避免在where子句中对字段进行函数操作，这将导致引擎放弃使用索引而进行全表扫描。如：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where substring(name,1,3)=&#39;abc&#39;--name以abc开头的id<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">应改为:<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select id from t where name like &#39;abc%&#39;<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">9.不要在 where 子句中的“=”左边进行函数、算术运算或其他表达式运算，否则系统将可能无法正确使用索引。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">10.在使用索引字段作为条件时，如果该索引是复合索引，那么必须使用到该索引中的第一个字段作为条件时才能保证系统使用该索引，<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">否则该索引将不会被使用，并且应尽可能的让字段顺序与索引顺序相一致。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">11.不要写一些没有意义的查询，如需要生成一个空表结构：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select col1,col2 into #t from t where 1=0<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">这类代码不会返回任何结果集，但是会消耗系统资源的，应改成这样：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">create table #t(...)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">12.很多时候用 exists 代替 in 是一个好的选择：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select num from a where num in(select num from b)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">用下面的语句替换：<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">select num from a where exists(select 1 from b where num=a.num)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">13.并不是所有索引对查询都有效，SQL是根据表中数据来进行查询优化的，当索引列有大量数据重复时，SQL查询可能不会去利用索引，<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">如一表中有字段sex，male、female几乎各一半，那么即使在sex上建了索引也对查询效率起不了作用。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">14.索引并不是越多越好，索引固然可以提高相应的 select 的效率，但同时也降低了 insert 及 update 的效率，<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">因为 insert 或 update 时有可能会重建索引，所以怎样建索引需要慎重考虑，视具体情况而定。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">一个表的索引数最好不要超过6个，若太多则应考虑一些不常使用到的列上建的索引是否有必要。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">15.尽量使用数字型字段，若只含数值信息的字段尽量不要设计为字符型，这会降低查询和连接的性能，并会增加存储开销。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">这是因为引擎在处理查询和连接时会逐个比较字符串中每一个字符，而对于数字型而言只需要比较一次就够了。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">16.尽可能的使用 varchar 代替 char ，因为首先变长字段存储空间小，可以节省存储空间，<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">其次对于查询来说，在一个相对较小的字段内搜索效率显然要高些。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">17.任何地方都不要使用 select * from t ，用具体的字段列表代替“*”，不要返回用不到的任何字段。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">18.避免频繁创建和删除临时表，以减少系统表资源的消耗。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">19.临时表并不是不可使用，适当地使用它们可以使某些例程更有效，例如，当需要重复引用大型表或常用表中的某个数据集时。但是，对于一次性事件，最好使用导出表。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">20.在新建临时表时，如果一次性插入数据量很大，那么可以使用 select into 代替 create table，避免造成大量 log ，<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">以提高速度；如果数据量不大，为了缓和系统表的资源，应先create table，然后insert。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">21.如果使用到了临时表，在存储过程的最后务必将所有的临时表显式删除，先 truncate table ，然后 drop table ，这样可以避免系统表的较长时间锁定。<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">22.尽量避免使用游标，因为游标的效率较差，如果游标操作的数据超过1万行，那么就应该考虑改写。</span><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; white-space: pre;\">	</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">23.使用基于游标的方法或临时表方法之前，应先寻找基于集的解决方案来解决问题，基于集的方法通常更有效。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">24.与临时表一样，游标并不是不可使用。对小型数据集使用 FAST_FORWARD 游标通常要优于其他逐行处理方法，尤其是在必须引用几个表才能获得所需的数据时。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">在结果集中包括“合计”的例程通常要比使用游标执行的速度快。如果开发时间允许，基于游标的方法和基于集的方法都可以尝试一下，看哪一种方法的效果更好。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">25.尽量避免大事务操作，提高系统并发能力。26.尽量避免向客户端返回大数据量，若数据量过大，应该考虑相应需求是否合理。</p>', '3', 'checked', '', '2019-03-13 15:42:26', '5', '12', '2019-03-13 15:42:26');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('59', 'Redis面试必知必会', 'Redis 支持哪几种数据类型?', null, '/upload/article/20190313155146.jpg', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis 支持哪几种数据类型?</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">string：最基本的数据类型，二进制安全的字符串，最大512M</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">list：按照添加顺序保持顺序的 字符串列表</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">set：无序的字符串集合，不存在重复的元素</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">sorted set：已排序的字符串集合</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">hash：key/value对的一种集合</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis是单进程的还是单线程的？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis是单进程单线程的，Redis利用队列技术将并发访问变为串行访问，消除了传统数据库串行控制的开销。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis为什么是单线程的？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">多线程处理会设计到锁，而且多线程处理会设计到线程切换而消耗CPU。因为CPU不会Redis的瓶颈，Redis的瓶颈最有可能是机器内存或者网络带宽。单线程无法发挥多核CPU性能，不过可以通过在单机开启Redis实例来解决。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis的优势</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">速度快。因为数据存储于内存中，类似于HashMap，HashMap的优势就是查找和操作的时间复杂度都是O(1)</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">支持丰富的数据类型，支持string，list，set，sorted set，hash</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">支持事务，操作都是原子性，所谓的原子性就是对数据的更改要么全部执行，要么全部不执行</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">丰富的特性：可用于缓存，消息，按key设置过期时间，过期后将会自动删除</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis和memcached有哪些优势</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">memcached所有的值均是简单的字符串，Reids作为其替代者，支持更为丰富的数据类型</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis的速度比memcached快很多</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis可以持久化其数据</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis支持数据的备份，即master/slave模式的数据备份</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis有哪几种数据淘汰策略</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">在Redis中，允许用户设置最大使用内存大小server.maxmemory，当Redis内存数据集大小上升到一定大小的时候，就会执行数据淘汰策略</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">volatile-lru：从已设置过期的数据集中挑选最近最少使用的淘汰</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">volatile-ttl：从已设置过期的数据集中挑选将要过期的数据淘汰</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">volatile-random：从已设置过期的数据集中任意挑选数据淘汰</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">allkeys-lru：从数据集中挑选最近最少使用的数据淘汰</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">allkeys-random：从数据集中任意挑选数据淘汰</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">noenviction：禁止淘汰数据</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis支持哪几种持久化方式</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">RDB持久化</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">原理是将Redis在内存中的数据记录定时dump到磁盘上的RDB文件</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">指定的时间间隔内将内存中的数据集快照写入磁盘，实际操作过程是fork一个子进程，先将数据集写入临时文件，写入成功后，再替换之前的文件，用二进制压缩存储。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">AOF（append only file）持久化</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">原理是将Redis的操作日志以追加的方式写入文件。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">以日志的形式记录服务器所处理的每一个写、删除操作，查询操作不会记录，以文本的方式记录，可以打开文件看到详细的操作记录。当服务器重启的时候会重新执行这些命令来恢复原始的数据。AOF命令以Reids协议追加保存每次写的操作到文件末尾。Redis还能对AOF文件进行后台重写，使得AOF文件的体积不至于过大。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis两种持久化方式优缺点？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">RDB持久化</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">优点：RDB文件紧凑，体积小，网络传输快，适合全量复制；恢复速度比AOF快很多。当然，与AOF相比，RDB最重要的优点之一是对性能的影响相对较小</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">缺点：RDB文件的致命缺点在与其数据快照的持久化方式决定了必然做不到实时持久化，而在数据越来越重要的今天，数据的大量丢失很多时候是无法接受的，因此AOF持久化称为主流。此外，RDB文件需要满足特定格式，兼容性差。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">AOF持久化</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">与RDB持久化相对应,AOF的优点在于支持秒级持久化、兼容性好，缺点是文件大，恢复速度慢，对性能影响大</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">如何选择Redis持久化方式策略？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">在介绍持久化策略之前，首先要明白无论是RDB还是AOF，持久化的开启都是要付出性能方面的代价的。对比RDB持久化，一方面是bdsave在进行fork操作时Redis主进程会阻塞，另一方面，子进程向硬盘写数据也会带来IO压力；对于AOF持久化，向硬盘写数据的频率大大提高（everysec策略下为秒级），IO压力更大，设置可能造成AOF追加阻塞文件。此外，AOF文件的重写与RDB的basave类似，会有fork时的阻塞和子进程的IO压力问题。相对来说，由于AOF向硬盘中写数据的频率更高，因此对Redis主进程性能的影响会更大。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">在实际生产环境中，根据数据量、应用对数据的安全要求、预算限制等不同情况，会有各种各样的持久化策略；如完全不使用任何持久化，使用RDB或AOF一种，或同事开启RDB和AOF持久化等。此外，持久化的选择必须与Redis的主从策略一起考虑，因为主从复制与持久化同样具有数据备份的功能，而且主机master和从机slave可以独立的选择持久化方案。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis集群的主从复制模型是怎样的？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">为了是在部分节点失败或者大部分节点无法通信的情况下集群仍然可用，所以集群是用了主从复制模型，每个节点都会有N-1个复制品</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis集群会有写操作丢失吗？为什么？</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis并不能保证数据强一致性，这意味着在实际中集群在特定的条件下可能会丢失写操作</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis集群之间是如何复制的</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">异步复制</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis如何做内存优化</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">尽可能使用散列表（hashes），散列表（是说列表里面存储的数少）使用的内存非常小，所以你应该尽可能的将你的数据模型抽象到一个散列表里面，比如你的web系统中有一个用户对象，不要为这个用户的名称，姓氏，邮箱，密码设置单独的key，而是应该把这个用户所有信息存储到一张散列表中</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Redis回收进程如何工作？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">一个Client运行了新的命令，添加了新的数据，Redis会检查内存使用情况，如果大于maxmemory的限制，则根据设定好的策略进行回收</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Redis常用的使用场景</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">Session共享（单点登录）</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">页面缓存</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">队列</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">排行榜/计算器</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">发布/订阅</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text